net.algem.planning
Class ScheduleRange

java.lang.Object
  net.algem.planning.ScheduleRange
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class ScheduleRange
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Schedule range entity. A range is included in a schedule. In UML, it's a composition. A range is linked to a schedule and a schedule may include several ranges. To facilitate certain operations, some schedule characteristics are retrieved at the range level (teacher, room, course,...).

Since:
1.0a 07/07/1999
